    "title": {
      "rendered": "How to Create a Twitter Moment for Your Nonprofit"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><strong><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/How-to-Create-a-Twitter-Moment-for-Your-Nonprofit-Square.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-20237\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/How-to-Create-a-Twitter-Moment-for-Your-Nonprofit-Square-300x300.png?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"how-to-create-a-twitter-moment-for-your-nonprofit-square\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/How-to-Create-a-Twitter-Moment-for-Your-Nonprofit-Square.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/How-to-Create-a-Twitter-Moment-for-Your-Nonprofit-Square.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/How-to-Create-a-Twitter-Moment-for-Your-Nonprofit-Square.png?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/How-to-Create-a-Twitter-Moment-for-Your-Nonprofit-Square.png?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/How-to-Create-a-Twitter-Moment-for-Your-Nonprofit-Square.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/How-to-Create-a-Twitter-Moment-for-Your-Nonprofit-Square.png?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/twittermoments\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter Moments</a></strong> as defined by Twitter are curated tweets collected into a story. First launched in October 2015 in partnership with a select few media partners, as of September 29 all Twitter users can now create Moments. For nonprofits active on Twitter,\u00a0Moments are new way to showcase the best tweets about your event or campaign. Moments are meant predominately for live reporting and mobile consumption. You&#8217;ll either have a Moment that looks great in Mobile (vertical images and videos) or\u00a0a Moment better viewed on a desktop (square and rectangle images in full size).</p>\n<p>For the <strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\" target=\"_blank\">International Fundraising Congress 2016 Moment</a></strong> desktop was prioritized. If possible, view the Moment on both desktop and mobile before experimenting with creating your own Moment. That said, creating Moments has a learning curve. Use the nine steps steps detailed below to guide your nonprofit when creating its first Twitter Moment.</p>\n<h1>1. Go to Moments &gt; Create new Moment.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20204\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-1-1.png?resize=600%2C222\" alt=\"moment-1-1\" width=\"600\" height=\"222\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-1-1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-1-1.png?resize=300%2C111&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=600%2C17\" alt=\"spacer2\" width=\"600\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=300%2C9&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">2. Add a Moment title and description.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20208\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-2.png?resize=600%2C369\" alt=\"moment-2\" width=\"600\" height=\"369\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-2.png?resize=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=600%2C17\" alt=\"spacer2\" width=\"600\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=300%2C9&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1>3. Create a custom Moment cover sized to be\u00a0compatible with desktop (1000 x 1000) and mobile (1000 X 575 when cropped).</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20207\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IFC2016-Moment-Cover-Photo-22.jpg?resize=600%2C600\" alt=\"ifc2016-moment-cover-photo-22\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IFC2016-Moment-Cover-Photo-22.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IFC2016-Moment-Cover-Photo-22.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IFC2016-Moment-Cover-Photo-22.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IFC2016-Moment-Cover-Photo-22.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IFC2016-Moment-Cover-Photo-22.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=600%2C17\" alt=\"spacer2\" width=\"600\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=300%2C9&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">4. Upload and review your custom Moment cover for desktop and mobile.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20211\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-3.png?resize=600%2C305\" alt=\"moment-3\" width=\"600\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-3.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-3.png?resize=300%2C153&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><br />\n</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20212\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-4.png?resize=600%2C297\" alt=\"moment-4\" width=\"600\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-4.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-4.png?resize=300%2C149&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><br />\n</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20213\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-5.png?resize=600%2C297\" alt=\"moment-5\" width=\"600\" height=\"297\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-5.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-5.png?resize=300%2C149&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=600%2C17\" alt=\"spacer2\" width=\"600\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=300%2C9&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1>5. Add tweets to your moment by selecting tweets (\u2714\ufe0f)\u00a0you have tweeted or liked or by conducting a search.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20215\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-6.png?resize=600%2C419\" alt=\"moments-6\" width=\"600\" height=\"419\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-6.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-6.png?resize=300%2C210&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=600%2C17\" alt=\"spacer2\" width=\"600\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=300%2C9&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">6. Rearrange tweets in your preferred order by selecting up or down arrows.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20216\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-8.png?resize=600%2C445\" alt=\"moments-8\" width=\"600\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-8.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-8.png?resize=300%2C223&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=600%2C17\" alt=\"spacer2\" width=\"600\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=300%2C9&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">7. When finished, select Publish. You will then be prompted to crop photos for mobile. You can crop all photos at once with one click or select each photo individually. Only crop images that are compatible with mobile.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20217\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-9.png?resize=600%2C316\" alt=\"moments-9\" width=\"600\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-9.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-9.png?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">For example, this image is not compatible for cropping.</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20218\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-11.png?resize=600%2C336\" alt=\"moments-11\" width=\"600\" height=\"336\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-11.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-11.png?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><br />\n</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20219\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-10.png?resize=600%2C333\" alt=\"moments-10\" width=\"600\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-10.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-10.png?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=600%2C17\" alt=\"spacer2\" width=\"600\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=300%2C9&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">8. Publish and tweet Moment (\u26a1)\u00a0with your Moment cover photo attached. Add location, if applicable.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20224\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-14.png?resize=600%2C381\" alt=\"moments-14\" width=\"600\" height=\"381\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-14.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-14.png?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/nonprofitorgs/status/789339876961427456\" target=\"_blank\">View Published Moment</a></h1>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Alternatively, publish your Moment with an auto-generated cover photo (no image attached to the tweet).</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20226\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-13.png?resize=600%2C218\" alt=\"moments-13\" width=\"600\" height=\"218\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-13.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moments-13.png?resize=300%2C109&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/nonprofitorgs/status/790135510543073280\" target=\"_blank\">View Published Moment (Auto-Generated Cover)</a></h2>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=600%2C17\" alt=\"spacer2\" width=\"600\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=300%2C9&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">9.\u00a0Edit your Moment, if necessary. Note that after you have published a Moment, you can only add tweets that you have &#8220;Liked\u00a0\u2764\ufe0f&#8221;. Your liked tweets are located at the end of your Moment. To add tweets, repeat steps 5 and 6 above.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20230\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-111.jpg?resize=600%2C264\" alt=\"moment-111\" width=\"600\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-111.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-111.jpg?resize=300%2C132&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20231\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-112.jpg?resize=600%2C234\" alt=\"moment-112\" width=\"600\" height=\"234\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-112.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-112.jpg?resize=300%2C117&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/moments/789024560532291584\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20232\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-113.jpg?resize=600%2C206\" alt=\"moment-113\" width=\"600\" height=\"206\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-113.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Moment-113.jpg?resize=300%2C103&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20159\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=600%2C17\" alt=\"spacer2\" width=\"600\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Spacer2.jpg?resize=300%2C9&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
      "rendered": "<p>Twitter Moments as defined by Twitter are curated tweets collected into a story. First launched in October 2015 in partnership with a select few media partners, as of September 29 all Twitter users can now create Moments. For nonprofits active on Twitter,\u00a0Moments are new way to showcase the best tweets about your event or campaign. Moments are meant predominately for live reporting and mobile consumption. You&#8217;ll either have a Moment that looks great in Mobile (vertical images and videos) or\u00a0a Moment better viewed on a desktop (square and rectangle images in full size). For the International Fundraising Congress 2016 Moment </p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
